## Phase 1 — Database & Scripture Foundation (Days 3–6)

### Goals
Define the database schema and seed it with curated Hindu scriptures.

### Database Schema (Prisma)

```prisma
model User {
  id              String   @id @default(uuid())
  phone           String   @unique
  name            String?
  rashi           String?              // Mesh, Vrishabh, Mithun, etc.
  language        String   @default("en") // "en" | "hi"
  deliveryTime    String   @default("07:00")  // HH:mm IST
  timezone        String   @default("Asia/Kolkata")
  onboardingStep  Int      @default(0)
  isOnboarded     Boolean  @default(false)
  isPremium       Boolean  @default(false)
  streakCount     Int      @default(0)
  lastInteraction DateTime?
  createdAt       DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt       DateTime @updatedAt

  conversations   Conversation[]
  dailyMessages   DailyMessage[]
}

model Scripture {
  id            String   @id @default(uuid())
  source        String               // "Bhagavad Gita", "Ramayana", etc.
  reference     String               // "Chapter 2, Verse 47"
  textSanskrit  String?              // Original Sanskrit
  textEnglish   String               // English translation
  textHindi     String?              // Hindi translation
  tags          String[]             // ["strength", "karma", "devotion", ...]
  category      String?              // "mantra", "shloka", "stotra", "sutra"
  createdAt     DateTime @default(now())
}

model DailyMessage {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId      String
  user        User     @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id])
  date        DateTime @db.Date
  horoscope   String
  verseId     String?
  verseText   String
  challenge   String
  sentAt      DateTime?
  opened      Boolean  @default(false)
  replied     Boolean  @default(false)
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
}

model Conversation {
  id        String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId    String
  user      User     @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id])
  role      String               // "user" | "assistant"
  content   String
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
}
```

### Scripture Curation
Curate **60+ verses** from Hindu scriptures, tagged by theme:

| Source | Target Count | Example Tags |
|---|---|---|
| Bhagavad Gita | 25 | karma, dharma, detachment, strength, devotion |
| Upanishads | 10 | self-knowledge, truth, consciousness |
| Ramayana | 10 | duty, courage, loyalty, family |
| Hanuman Chalisa | 5 | devotion, protection, strength |
| Vedas / Mantras | 5 | peace, prosperity, gratitude |
| Puranas / Stotras | 5 | faith, surrender, divine grace |

Format: JSON files in `data/scriptures/` → imported via seed script.

#### Tasks
- [ ] Write `prisma/schema.prisma`
- [ ] Run `prisma migrate dev` to create tables
- [ ] Create `data/scriptures/bhagavad_gita.json`, `upanishads.json`, etc.
- [ ] Write `scripts/seed-scriptures.js` to import verses into DB
- [ ] Verify: query DB to confirm verse count and tag distribution

