## Phase 5 — Web Dashboard (Days 27–34)

### Goals
Build a modern, visually stunning Next.js dashboard for user registration, profile management, and streak/history viewing.

### Pages

| Route | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `/` | Landing page — product pitch, sign-up CTA |
| `/signup` | Alternative registration (phone verification via OTP) |
| `/dashboard` | Profile overview, current streak, today's message |
| `/history` | Past daily messages in a feed/timeline view |
| `/settings` | Edit rashi, language, delivery time |

### Design Direction
- **Dark theme** with saffron/gold accent (#FF9933, #FFD700)
- Glassmorphism cards for daily messages
- Sanskrit-inspired typography (Google Fonts: Yatra One for headings, Inter for body)
- Smooth micro-animations (streak fire animation, verse fade-in)
- Fully responsive (mobile-first)

### API Endpoints (Backend)

| Method | Route | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/auth/send-otp` | Send OTP to phone |
| POST | `/api/auth/verify-otp` | Verify OTP, return JWT |
| GET | `/api/user/profile` | Get user profile |
| PUT | `/api/user/profile` | Update preferences |
| GET | `/api/user/streak` | Current streak + history |
| GET | `/api/messages` | Paginated daily message history |
| GET | `/api/messages/:id` | Single message detail |

#### Tasks
- [ ] Build API auth routes (OTP-based phone auth with JWT)
- [ ] Build API data routes (profile, streak, messages)
- [ ] Design and build landing page (`/`)
- [ ] Build sign-up page with OTP flow
- [ ] Build dashboard page (streak display, today's message)
- [ ] Build history page (timeline of past messages)
- [ ] Build settings page
- [ ] Test: full sign-up → dashboard → history flow in browser

