## Post-MVP Roadmap (V2)

| Feature | Description | Priority |
|---|---|---|
| Monthly Challenges | 40-day Hanuman Chalisa, Navratri 9-day, Shiva month | High |
| Community Responses | See anonymized responses to today's challenge | High |
| Spiritual Journal | Reply with gratitude; bot reflects them back weekly | Medium |
| Audio Mantras | Voice messages of mantras/shlokas with daily text | Medium |
| Multi-language | Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, Gujarati, Marathi | Medium |
| Family/Group Plans | Shared family streaks and challenges | Low |
| Festival Calendar | Automated special messages on Hindu festivals | High |
| Panchang Integration | Tithi, nakshatra, muhurat in daily messages | Medium |
